title: Bye Bye Binary: Thought's on Teen Vogue's latest video
description:
Teen Vogue put out a video explaining how binary framework for male and female is not, in fact...well...fact. I have some thoughts. 

I reference a previous interview of mine with evolutionary biologist Colin Wright, you can see our full interview here
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cK49Y9kz_ek

Follow me here:

twitter: @theother_95
Instagram: @theother95
Facebook: @theother95page
Email me: theotherninetyfive@gmail.com
